flowchart TD
    subgraph MH02["MH-02: Pre-session Check-in User Flow"]
        C1[APScheduler triggers 12-24h before] --> C2[Notification Service sends Telegram push]
        C2 --> C3[User receives message with inline buttons]
        C3 --> C4{User responds?}
        C4 -->|Tap emoji| C5["😊 Good | 😐 Okay | 😔 Low"]
        C4 -->|Skip| C6[No penalty, recorded as skipped]
        C4 -->|Ignore| C7[Reminder in 4h]
        C5 --> C8{Add text?}
        C8 -->|Yes| C9[User types state description]
        C8 -->|No| C10[Save emoji only]
        C9 --> C11[Save to State Service]
        C10 --> C11
        C11 --> C12[Confirmation message sent]
    end
